00:53:53,180 --> 00:53:56,507
hidden scroll. That's a very dangerous idea. One of the 39 מלאכות

1116
00:53:56,507 --> 00:53:59,460
*melachos* you're not חייב מיתה chayav misa. *chayav misa*. So which one

1117
00:53:59,460 --> 00:54:01,940
is it? We don't know. So רב יהודה פשיטא ליה *Rav Yehuda

1118
00:54:01,940 --> 00:54:05,820
pshita leh*, so for רב יהודה *Rav Yehuda* who said that the

1119
00:54:05,820 --> 00:54:06,640
מקושש *mekoshesh*

1120
00:54:07,920 --> 00:54:12,000
was carrying, for him it's obvious דהמעביר חייב *de'hama'avir chayav*, that carrying

1121
00:54:12,000 --> 00:54:16,740
is not that one. That carrying is definitely חייב *chayav*, it's not

1122
00:54:16,740 --> 00:54:19,620
the one of the 39 that איסי בן יהודה *Isi ben Yehuda*

1123
00:54:19,620 --> 00:54:22,500
says it's not חייב מיתה *chayav misa*. ומתניתא פשיטא ליה *U'masnisa pshita

1124
00:54:22,500 --> 00:54:24,740
leh*, the ברייתא *braisa* that says that what he did was he

1125
00:54:24,740 --> 00:54:28,280
uprooted something that was growing, דתולש חייב *detolesh chayav*. It's obvious that

1126
00:54:28,280 --> 00:54:31,820
תולש *tolesh* is certainly not the one that you would be exempt

1127
00:54:31,820 --> 00:54:34,093
for, that you would not be חייב מיתה *chayav misa*. ולרב אחא

1128
00:54:34,093 --> 00:54:36,627
בר יעקב פשיטא ליה *U'leRav Achah bar Yaakov pshita leh*, and for

1129
00:54:36,627 --> 00:54:38,147
רב אחא בר יעקב *Rav Achah bar Yaakov* it's obvious to him

1130
00:54:38,147 --> 00:54:41,660
דמעמר חייב *dem'amer chayav*. That מעמר *ma'amer* is the—is definitely חייב *chayav*

1131
00:54:41,660 --> 00:54:43,607
and is not one of the ones that might not be. מר

1132
00:54:43,607 --> 00:54:46,185
סבר הא מילתא לא מספקא ליה *Mar savar ha milta lo mesapka

1133
00:54:46,185 --> 00:54:47,780
leh*. One says this at least was not under doubt. ומר סבר

1134
00:54:47,780 --> 00:54:50,072
הא מילתא לא מספקא ליה *Umar savar ha milta lo mesapka leh*.

1135
00:54:50,072 --> 00:54:50,700
And the other says his was at least not under doubt. But

1136
00:54:50,700 --> 00:54:53,320
by the way, this is an important thing to be bringing up

1137
00:54:53,320 --> 00:54:57,240
here, because after just having said about how carrying is such a

1138
00:54:57,240 --> 00:55:00,540
different type of a מלאכה *melacha*, if somebody told you... one of

1139
00:55:00,540 --> 00:55:04,200
the מלאכות you're not חייב מיתה for, guess which one? I think

1140
00:55:04,200 --> 00:55:06,820
we all would have assumed that carrying would have been that. It

1141
00:55:06,820 --> 00:55:10,140
seems to be the most, the most different of all of them

1142
00:55:10,140 --> 00:55:13,020
as we've been saying. But here the גמרא ends by saying that

1143
00:55:13,020 --> 00:55:16,860
at least according to those that understand the מקושש was carrying, it

1144
00:55:16,860 --> 00:55:18,620
is not the one. And this is only of course according to

1145
00:55:18,620 --> 00:55:21,040
איסי בן יהודה. It's not how we rule. We rule that every

1146
00:55:21,040 --> 00:55:24,440
single one of the thirty-nine is חייב מיתה. We will continue tomorrow

1147
00:55:24,520 --> 00:55:26,020
with the story of מקושש.
